by Nicofuma at 2017-09-19T12:15:16Z

With `@grep -E '(^[a-zA-Z_-]+:.*?##.*$$)|(^##)' $(MAKEFILE_LIST) | awk 'BEGIN {FS = ":.*?## "}; {printf "\033[32m%-30s\033[0m %s\n", $$1, $$2}' | sed -e 's/\[32m##/[33m/'` you can add sections and you will also have colors close to the bin/console ones.

Ex with sections:
```
#
## Section 1
##---------------------------------------------------------------------------

target1:          ## target one

#
## Section 2
##---------------------------------------------------------------------------

target2:          ## target two
target2: target1
```
